{"tid":988844,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"譚詠麟 昨晚上海演唱會唱：你知我知","createTime":"2019-01-20T12:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T12:12:39.000Z","uid":230125,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea5f6d4067dfd77e592f01353459c9bebe78bda","tid":988844,"uid":230125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"昨晚，譚詠麟銀河歲月演唱會上海站開場曲：你知我知<a href=\"http://f.us.sinaimg.cn/003MFfGQlx07qTCvJ0BG01041202xue20E010.mp4?label=hongbaofly_2019&amp;template=852x480.28.0&amp;Expires=1547987100&amp;ssig=kfYD8TadlA&amp;KID=unistore,video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ff.us.sinaimg.cn%2F003MFfGQlx07qTCvJ0BG01041202xue20E010.mp4%3Flabel%3Dhongbaofly_2019%26template%3D852x480.28.0%26Expires%3D1547987100%26ssig%3DkfYD8TadlA%26KID%3Dunistore%2Cvideo&d=jaV%2BRe3y%2FXUob74I7FcGrJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1b364934\" target=\"_blank\">http://f.us.sinaimg.cn/003MFfGQlx07qTCvJ0BG01041202xue20E010.mp4?label=hongbaofly_2019&amp;template=852x480.28.0&amp;Expires=1547987100&amp;ssig=kfYD8TadlA&amp;KID=unistore,video</a><br />\n下午有在fb直播這part綵排<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alan.tamwinglun/videos/1028871127236509/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falan.tamwinglun%2Fvideos%2F1028871127236509%2F&d=jaV%2BRe3y%2FXUob74I7FcGrJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=799d0272\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/alan.tamwinglun/videos/1028871127236509/</a> <br />\n<br />\n近年成日有d人想太多，用自己的FF去抹黑別人，好多人話過Alan Tam一定唔會再唱這首歌...<br />\n但其實，他199x﹑200x﹑201x都有在大陸唱過這首。<br />\n我覺得坊間好多人云亦云亂咁扣他帽子，其實他有時講d野根本就是好大路他那一代很多人的大路思維，都無什麼政治化，亦冇擦鞋，我家d長輩好多都是差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n順便重温：<br />\n25+14歲的版本，最後高音那part超級強<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qe4yRGwkKIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqe4yRGwkKIQ&d=jaV%2BRe3y%2FXUob74I7FcGrJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=264fb4ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qe4yRGwkKIQ</a> <br />\n<br />\n現在25+43歲，雖然後面那part比以前降了key, 這年紀我覺得已經好好。<br />\n<br />\n不過，如果昨晚快歌計，他唱這首他自己作曲的&quot;知心當玩偶&quot;表現更佳。<br />\n<a href=\"http://f.us.sinaimg.cn/002rkXarlx07qUQmgDUI01041201H3EZ0E010.mp4?label=hongbaofly_2019&amp;template=852x480.28.0&amp;Expires=1547987654&amp;ssig=dVsSawDLih&amp;KID=unistore,video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ff.us.sinaimg.cn%2F002rkXarlx07qUQmgDUI01041201H3EZ0E010.mp4%3Flabel%3Dhongbaofly_2019%26template%3D852x480.28.0%26Expires%3D1547987654%26ssig%3DdVsSawDLih%26KID%3Dunistore%2Cvideo&d=jaV%2BRe3y%2FXUob74I7FcGrJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=07926095\" target=\"_blank\">http://f.us.sinaimg.cn/002rkXarlx07qUQmgDUI01041201H3EZ0E010.mp4?label=hongbaofly_2019&amp;template=852x480.28.0&amp;Expires=1547987654&amp;ssig=dVsSawDLih&amp;KID=unistore,video</a>"}]}